<% provide(:title, "Hi") %>

<section class="header-home">
    <h1 class="header-home__title">OddEats Dublin</h1>
    <h2 class="header-home__subtitle">Lorem ipsum ammet dolores</h2>
</section>

<section class="home-intro">
    <h2 class="home-intro__title">OddEats, what's the story?</h2>
    <p class="home-intro__text">Its 2019, the era of anything goes it seems. People have become increasingly adventurous, moral, disciplined and oftentimes, quite restricted in terms of their diets. People have always worked hard on their diets with the intention of losing weight, with salad being the obvious choice of breakfast, lunch and dinner which.</p>
</section>

<section class="home-slider">
